 Installation:

    git clone git@bitbucket.org:korpz/dotvim.git

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/.vimrc ~/.vimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update

To add new plugins as submodules

cd ~/.vim
mkdir ~/.vim/bundle
git submodule add http://github.com/test/vim-test.git bundle/test
git add .
git commit -m "Install new bundle"
